- **Quick Actions**:
  - "Add to Cart" button on product cards
  - "Add to Wishlist" button on product cards
  - Buttons use `event.stopPropagation()` to prevent modal opening
- **Utilities**:
  - `escapeHtml()` - XSS prevention for text content
  - `escapeUrl()` - URL encoding for share links
